method.description:
Gets debug information about shared voxel processing.
The returned dictionary has the following structure:
[codeblock]
{
	"streaming": {
		"tasks": int,
		"active_threads": int,
		"thread_count": int
	},
	"meshing": {
		"tasks": int,
		"active_threads": int,
		"thread_count": int
	}
}
[/codeblock]
